OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1779451870
OL,3,CMan who dug up more than a kilogram of
OL,4,Ccocaine jailed
OL,6,FA man who dug up cocaine worth up to
OL,7,F#300,000 in a Jersey woodland has been
OL,8,Fjailed for six-and-a-half years by the
OL,9,Fisland's Royal Court.
OL,11,FJamie Lagadu, 24, was caught
OL,12,Fcollecting a bag of the Class A drug,
OL,13,Fwhich weighed 1.35 kilograms, in the
OL,14,FGrands Vaux area of St Saviour on 20
OL,15,FNovember last year.
OL,17,FHe then took a small amount of the
OL,18,Fsubstance for himself before reburying
OL,19,Fthe rest.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
