FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1779451870
OL,3,CMan who dug up more than a kilogram of
OL,4,Ccocaine jailed
OL,6,FAlmost a fortnight before that, police
OL,7,Fsurveillance cameras showed Lagadu and
OL,8,Fanother man talking about where to
OL,9,Ffind a bag of drugs behind a
OL,10,Fconvenience shop in the area.
OL,12,FLagadu was arrested as police officers
OL,13,Fhid 20 metres away from the buried
OL,14,Fcocaine and waited for him to return.
OL,16,FWhen he was stopped with three grams
OL,17,Fof cocaine, the 24-year-old claimed he
OL,18,Fhad bought it before officers revealed
OL,19,Fthey knew about the stash.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1779451870
OL,3,CMan who dug up more than a kilogram of
OL,4,Ccocaine jailed
OL,6,FWhen questioned by officers, Lagadu
OL,7,Fsaid he had been asked by someone to
OL,8,Fcheck on the drugs in exchange for a
OL,9,Fsmall amount of cocaine.
OL,11,FHowever, when the police asked Lagadu
OL,12,Ffor his mobile phone passcode, he
OL,13,Frefused to tell them.
OL,15,FThe defence argued this was in fear of
OL,16,Frevealing the identity of the other
OL,17,Fperson who was "further up the chain".
OL,19,FThe Court also heard that Lagadu has
OL,20,Fmental health and substance issues and
OL,21,Fexperienced childhood trauma.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1779451870
OL,3,CMan who dug up more than a kilogram of
OL,4,Ccocaine jailed
OL,6,FIn his summary remarks, Jersey Bailiff
OL,7,FRobert MacRae said Lagadu's
OL,8,Funwillingness to assist the police
OL,9,Fwith access to his device had
OL,10,F"frustrated" their investigation.
OL,12,FThe States of Jersey Police say this
OL,13,Fcase highlights the extreme lengths
OL,14,Fcriminals will go to conceal drugs.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Hafey,
OL,17,Ffrom the force, adds: "Criminals are
OL,18,Fbecoming more sophisticated.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1779451870
OL,3,CMan who dug up more than a kilogram of
OL,4,Ccocaine jailed
OL,6,F"I think what this case shows is that
OL,7,Fthere was a degree of organisation
OL,8,Fhere - the fact that the drugs hadn't
OL,9,Fjust been casually hidden, there'd
OL,10,Fbeen time, effort and planning that
OL,11,Fhad gone into hiding the drugs in
OL,12,Fcertain locations, which made the
OL,13,Fsurveillance even harder."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
